      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5927134/" class="title-link">国难当头之时，你会是谁？你想成为谁？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5927134"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1345666/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1345666-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1345666/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">落落樱花</span>
