  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7581405/" class="title-link">从《四世同堂》看老舍创作思想的矛盾性</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7581405"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/8810763/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u8810763-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/8810763/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">猫豆小漾</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-08-26"
      class="main-meta">2015-08-26 16:11:30</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7581405_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                        老舍是地道的北平人，从小在胡同中长大，耳濡目染北平文化是必然的，之后他去英国当中文讲师的时候开始真正意义上的文化批判写作，同鲁迅一样，作品旨在拯救国民的灵魂，改造国民性，但是他们的批判方式又是不一样的。在《四世同堂》中，老舍对北平人身上所体现出的懦弱...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7581405/#comments">(9回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">24有用 / 1没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            北京出版社2005版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
